g.wiki.fextralife.com/Spelldrake+Talisman">Spelldrake Talisman</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Stalwart+Horn+Charm">Stalwart Horn Charm</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Starscourge+Heirloom">Starscourge Heirloom</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Taker's+Cameo">Taker's Cameo</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Twinblade+Talisman">Twinblade Talisman</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Two+Fingers+Heirloom">Two Fingers Heirloom</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Viridian+Amber+Medallion">Viridian Amber Medallion</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Warrior+Jar+Shard">Warrior Jar Shard</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;♦&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class= "wiki_link" href="//eldenring.wiki.fextralife.com/Winged+Sword+Insignia">Winged Sword Insignia</a></div></td> 
